### List all foods as a JSON response
GET http://localhost:3000/menu

### Update specified food by id in url
PUT http://localhost:3000/menu/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Steak",
    "price": 129,
}

### Add a new food to the menu
POST http://localhost:3000/menu
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Steak", 
    "price": 149,
}

### Delete specified food by id in url
DELETE http://localhost:3000/menu/1

